This paper discusses the emerging cybersecurity issues in the automotive industry due to the digitalisation process and the transition to Mobility-as-a-Service. It focuses on the design of next-generation vehicles as complex cyber-physical systems that require a secure-by-design approach. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
